title: Learn Traditional Origami - Video Tutorials & Resources
description:
Learn Traditional Origami - Video Tutorials & Resources

Duration: 35m | Video: AVC (.MP4) 1280x720 30fps | Audio: AAC 44.1KHz 2ch | 914 MB
Genre: eLearning | Language: English

Master Origami classics in minutes with Videos Lessons including the Peace Crane, Lily, Frog, Butterfly and more
What are the requirements?
You'll need some paper to get started: Refer to our 'Origami Paper Recommendations' pdf
What am I going to get from this course?
Over 12 lectures and 52 mins of content!
Learn how to make 7 Traditional Origami Models: Peace Crane, Butterfly, Boat, Flapping Crane, Jumping Frog, Lily Flower & Star Box
Get Creative! Design or Colour-in your own Origami paper, with the help of the Origami Crease Patterns provided
What is the target audience?
You don't need any previous experience of Origami
The course is suitable for people of all ages
